00:45:33.910 --> 00:45:37.700
there was no constitution
yet -- to go ahead with this.

00:45:37.700 --> 00:45:41.990
This was the summer of 1787 and
they put the ordinance through.

00:45:41.990 --> 00:45:44.150
He did it -- one man.

00:45:44.150 --> 00:45:45.450
He did it.

00:45:45.450 --> 00:45:50.540
And the ordinance stipulated three
things of immense importance.

00:45:50.540 --> 00:45:53.090
It was one of the most
important bills ever passed

00:45:53.090 --> 00:45:57.060
by our congress even
before we had a president.

00:45:57.060 --> 00:45:59.300
One, there would be
complete freedom of religion,

00:45:59.300 --> 00:46:01.840
absolute complete freedom
of religion.

00:46:01.840 --> 00:46:05.370
The number two, the government
would be involved in education.

00:46:05.370 --> 00:46:09.250
There would public education
all the way through college.

00:46:09.250 --> 00:46:13.200
Hence, the beginning of the state
university system, for example.

00:46:13.200 --> 00:46:18.700
Third, and most important of
all, there would be no slavery.

00:46:18.700 --> 00:46:21.420
Now, what that meant --

00:46:21.420 --> 00:46:24.530
this territory was as big
as all the 13 colonies.

00:46:24.530 --> 00:46:27.060
There were slaves in every
one of the 13 colonies

00:46:27.060 --> 00:46:31.390
but it meant this new empire,
this wilderness empire,

00:46:31.390 --> 00:46:33.560
would be free to everyone.

00:46:33.560 --> 00:46:38.710 position:56%
All you had to do was get across the
Ohio River, the northwest territory

00:46:38.710 --> 00:46:42.910
and west of the Ohio River.

00:46:42.910 --> 00:46:46.620
It now constitutes the
states of Ohio, Indiana,

00:46:46.620 --> 00:46:49.750
Illinois, Michigan and Wisconsin.

00:46:49.750 --> 00:46:53.780
It's as big as all of
France, no slavery.

00:46:53.780 --> 00:46:56.420
So half of our country
would be no slavery.

00:46:56.420 --> 00:47:03.470
Imagine with one vote of congress,
one man put it through and

00:47:03.470 --> 00:47:07.000
yet I never knew anything about it,

00:47:07.000 --> 00:47:09.090
and most people know
nothing about it.

00:47:09.090 --> 00:47:14.010
